# Composition hierarchy

- **Atoms** must not import molecules, organisms, or stores
- **Molecules** compose atoms only — no organism imports
- **Organisms** may compose molecules and atoms; may access stores
- Do not skip layers (e.g. organism importing an atom for something a molecule should wrap)

When adding a component, pick the lowest layer that fits. See [src/components/AGENTS.md](src/components/AGENTS.md).
